5|$|Amrullah Saleh {{has been}} {{speaking}} and writing extensively {{on these issues}} in both local and international media. He maintains <b>that</b> <b>the</b> <b>Taliban</b> need to disarm and honor {{the integrity of the}} Afghan constitution before they could be considered for any reconciliation process.|$|E
5|$|On 9 March, Yousafzai {{wrote about}} a science paper that she {{performed}} well on, and added <b>that</b> <b>the</b> <b>Taliban</b> {{were no longer}} searching vehicles as they once did. Her blog ended on 12 March 2009.|$|E
