5000|$|Afghanistan President Karzai {{admitted}} that he spoke to <b>the</b> <b>Taliban</b> to bring about peace in Afghanistan. He noted <b>that</b> <b>the</b> Afghan <b>Taliban</b> are [...] "always welcome" [...] in Afghanistan, although foreign militants are not.|$|R
